Class EsxPreferenceStore

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.skratchdot.electribe.model.esx.preferences.EsxPreferenceStore

  • public class EsxPreferenceStore
extends java.lang.Object
    Provides getters for all the Open Electribe Editor preferences. A wrapper for calls to: PlatformUI.getPreferenceStore().getXXX()
